Is a RelationShip:

- It refers to the Inheritance.

- It means that one class is a specialized version of another class. The specialized class (subclass/child) inherits all the fields and behaviors of the more general class (superclass/parent).

Key Features:

1. Code reusablity

2. Polymorphism

3. Directional - Inheritance flows one way. A Car is a Vehicle, but a Vehicle is not necessarily a Car

